<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Mammoth Ride: Riders swing their mounts into Mammoth after a dusty ride 
from Bishop, Calif. Horsemen come from throughout the state to participate in 
the annual horse drive. JANE DOVE / For The Times 
</P>
