</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
What an excellent idea. I can't believe how blind our human race is. "Terminate 
pregnancy" -- please, just state the facts. To kill an unborn human being 
because of his or her place of residence, the mother's womb. 
</P>
