<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS: BANK EXECUTIVE NAMED TO URBAN LEAGUE BOARD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Esther Frankel, vice president and manager of Glendale Federal Bank's district 
sales center in Irvine, has been elected to the board of directors of the 
Orange County Urban League Inc. The league's programs include an employment 
service, a youth educational program and an advocacy and leadership development 
service for minorities and disadvantaged persons. 
</P>
