<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Robert C. Brosius has been named corporate director of quality management for 
MagneTek, Inc., and general manager of its program to supply electrical 
products for the national Superconducting Supercollider program. 
</P>
<P>
He was formerly general manger of the Los Angeles-based company's Anaheim 
facility. Brosius joined Magnetek in 1980 as director of contracts and 
marketing in Anaheim. Before that, he held marketing and management positions 
with Aeroject General and Rockwell International. 
</P>
