<P>
Bob Hope Donates $1 Million: Bob Hope has donated $1 million -- the largest 
individual contribution to date -- to the endowment fund for the Academy of 
Motion Pictures Arts and Sciences soon-to-be-completed Center for Motion 
Picture Study. 
</P>
<P>
