PHILIPPINES -- GOVERNMENT; PHILIPPINES -- POLITICS; GOVERNMENT MISCONDUCT; 
FRAUD; RACKETEERING; CONSPIRACY; KHASHOGGI, ADNAN; SUITS 
</P>
