<P>
In the Face of Fewer Marriages, More Divorces 
</P>
<P>
The U.S. traditionally has one of the highest marriage -- and divorce -- rates 
in the world. Now liberalized divorce laws are bringing a divorce boom in much 
of Europe. 
</P>
<P>
